{"tid":358771,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"救命啊 屋企無啦啦有小強啊！！！","createTime":"2017-08-14T02:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T07:01:43.000Z","uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ad5d0c68de44dc8b29d64dcf1ad45ca5cdef791","tid":358771,"uid":64787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:45:32.000Z","msg":"頭先屋企無啦啦有隻小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即噴殺蟲水搞掂<br />\n我好怕之後都keep住有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為呢到住左幾年，都冇半隻小強出現過<br />\n如果係個別事件都仲可以<br />\n但如果間唔時走一隻半隻出黎我會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇好多預防方法 都不外乎擺藥餌同小強屋<br />\n我擔心既係 如果屋企本身冇強<br />\n擺d藥餌同屋係到<br />\n會唔會間接引d小強埋黎<br />\n冇都變有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住直頭死左係d電器家俬後面睇唔見既地方<br />\n同條強屍一齊住<br />\n我真係會崩潰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇高手指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5cdd9ac54c1953e9d3445eebbeea5f5db6f704b","tid":358771,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:52:05.000Z","msg":"如果冇小朋友一齊住 就買個煙蛋<br />\n<br />\n炸佢老母冚家鏟啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066394df52f33c46deaaf945285e74c0e009b643","tid":358771,"uid":132680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先屋企無啦啦有隻小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即噴殺蟲水搞掂<br />\n我好怕之後都keep住有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為呢到住左幾年，都冇半隻小強出現過<br />\n如果係個別事件都仲可以<br />\n但如果間唔時走一隻半隻出黎我會痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上網睇好多預防方法 都不外乎擺藥餌同小強屋<br />\n我擔心既係 如果屋企本身冇強<br />\n擺d藥餌同屋係到<br />\n會唔會間接引d小強埋黎<br />\n冇都變有<img src=\"/